flowchart TB
    USER["User Sends a Text Message
    Example: 'Hey, how are you'"]

    USER --> BACKEND["Peppi Backend Receives the Message
    Identifies the user and their assigned buddy"]

    BACKEND --> GATHER["Gathers All Context to Build the AI Prompt
    Pulls from Database + AI Memory simultaneously"]

    GATHER --> DB["Peppi Database
    Stores user profiles, buddy profiles,
    daily routines, and chat history"]

    GATHER --> AI_MEMORY["AI Memory - Vector Search
    Searches past data using meaning-based matching
    to find the most relevant context for this message"]

    %% =================== BLOCK 1 ===================
    DB --> B1["Block 1: Response Rules
    ────────────────────
    Static text, same for every user
    ────────────────────
    KEEP ALL RESPONSES UNDER 200 TOKENS. HARD RULE.
    - Stop before 200 tokens. Always finish your sentence completely.
    - Short, casual, SMS-style. No walls of text.
    - Cut filler. Be direct. One or two sentences max.
    - Never trail off or get cut mid-thought.
    - DO NOT mention this limit."]

    %% =================== BLOCK 2 ===================
    DB --> B2["Block 2: User and Buddy Profiles + Instructions
    ────────────────────
    Pulled from database using user ID and buddy ID
    ────────────────────
    YOUR MISSION: Build a meaningful relationship through SMS conversations

    ABOUT ME (User Profile):
    Name: Tanmay Upasani, Age: 23, Male, American Indian
    Location: New York, NY, United States
    Hobbies: chess, cricket, singing, reading, startup
    Favorite foods: Pizza, biryani
    Current date/time and weather at user location

    ABOUT YOU (Buddy Profile):
    Relationship: Friend, Name: Jarvis, Age: 25, Male
    Location: New York, Education: Graduate degree
    Personality: Enthusiastic, Creative, Supportive
    Humor: Sarcastic and Playful, Language: English
    Current date/time and weather at buddy location

    LIFE STORY: Full multi-paragraph backstory from birth to present

    INSTRUCTIONS: Stay in character, relationship tone guide,
    how to text SMS-style, what not to do, crisis protocol,
    no medical/financial/sexual/illegal advice"]

    %% =================== BLOCK 3 ===================
    DB --> B3["Block 3: Buddy's Recent Daily Routines
    ────────────────────
    Last 2 days of schedules from database
    Filtered by: buddy ID + last 2 days
    Returns: 3 full day schedules
    ────────────────────
    Each day contains:
    - Date and summary of the day's mood
    - MORNING: wake up, breakfast, commute
    - WORK: office tasks, meetings, lunch
    - AFTERNOON: meetings, focus time, walks
    - EVENING: commute home, dinner, personal time
    - NIGHT: wind down, reading, sleep
    Each entry has exact time + activity detail

    Example: 2026-02-20, 2026-02-19, 2026-02-18

    Purpose: So buddy can casually mention what they did today"]

    %% =================== BLOCK 4 ===================
    DB --> B4["Block 4: Recent Chat History
    ────────────────────
    Last 25 messages between user and buddy from database
    Ordered by most recent first
    ────────────────────
    Format per message:
    Date: 2026-02-20T10:23:43.000000Z
    Tanmay Upasani: sure seeya bye
    Jarvis: yo catch you later man!

    Date: 2026-02-20T10:22:46.000000Z
    Tanmay Upasani: sorry i meant to say how many messages more do i have left to chat with you
    Jarvis: ah i dont actually have a limit on my end...

    Purpose: So buddy remembers what was just discussed"]

    %% =================== BLOCK 5 ===================
    AI_MEMORY --> B5["Block 5: Relevant Life Story Moments
    ────────────────────
    API: POST https://rag-api.dashtechs.com/api/v1/buddy/buddy/context
    Payload: { buddyId: 725, userUuid: eff67a70-..., query: 'Hey, how are you' }
    Response field used: data.storyChunks
    ────────────────────
    AI searches the buddy's full life story and returns
    the 5 most relevant chapters based on what the user said:

    STAGE_01: Early Childhood (age 0-5) - relevance: 0.618
    STAGE_02: Childhood (age 6-10) - relevance: 0.587
    STAGE_03: Childhood (age 11-15) - relevance: 0.592
    STAGE_04: Adolescence (age 16-20) - relevance: 0.607
    STAGE_05: Young Adult (age 21-25) - relevance: 0.611

    Each chunk: chunkId, full story text, age range, life phase, relevance score
    Inserted with prefix: 'Here is some information about the story:'"]

    %% =================== BLOCK 6 ===================
    AI_MEMORY --> B6["Block 6: Relevant Past Routines
    ────────────────────
    Same API call as Block 5 - single request returns both
    API: POST https://rag-api.dashtechs.com/api/v1/buddy/buddy/context
    Payload: { buddyId: 725, userUuid: eff67a70-..., query: 'Hey, how are you' }
    Response field used: data.routineChunks
    ────────────────────
    AI searches older daily schedules and returns
    the 5 most relevant past days:

    routine_725_2026-02-13: Friday - relevance: 0.617
    routine_725_2026-02-14: Saturday - relevance: 0.615
    routine_725_2026-02-11: Wednesday - relevance: 0.612
    routine_725_2026-02-15: Sunday - relevance: 0.610
    routine_725_2026-02-19: Thursday - relevance: 0.608

    Each chunk: full day schedule, date, day of week, summary, relevance score
    Inserted with prefix: 'Here is some information about the previous routine:'"]

    %% =================== BLOCK 7 ===================
    AI_MEMORY --> B7["Block 7: Relevant Past Conversations
    ────────────────────
    API: POST https://rag-pipeline.dashtechs.com/search
    Payload: {
      user_uuid: 'eff67a70-00f9-11f1-bbd8-ed635f290324',
      collection_name: 'peppi_chat_production',
      query: 'Hey, how are you',
      limit: 5
    }
    ────────────────────
    AI searches all past conversations and returns
    up to 5 batches of 15 messages each, ranked by similarity:

    Batch 1: similarity 0.694, from 2026-02-19 (15 messages)
    Batch 2: similarity 0.646, from 2026-02-03 (15 messages)
    Batch 3: similarity 0.636, from 2026-02-04 (15 messages)
    Batch 4: similarity 0.623, from 2026-02-04 (15 messages)

    Each batch: similarity score, full Q and A text, timestamp, memory type
    Inserted with prefix: 'Here are related past chats:'"]

    %% =================== BLOCK 8 ===================
    DB --> B8["Block 8: Current Moment + SMS Balance
    ────────────────────
    From system clock + database
    ────────────────────
    - Current date and time at user location
    - Current date and time at buddy location
    - Weather for both locations
    - How many SMS messages the user has remaining
    - Final reminder to stay under 200 tokens"]

    %% =================== ASSEMBLY ===================
    B1 -.-> B2 -.-> B3 -.-> B4 -.-> B5 -.-> B6 -.-> B7 -.-> B8

    B8 --> ASSEMBLED["All 8 Blocks Combined Into One Prompt
    ────────────────────
    Sent as an array:
    Index 0 = All 8 blocks concatenated as system context
    Index 1 = The user's actual message: 'Hey, how are you'"]

    ASSEMBLED --> LLM["AI Model Generates Response
    Using all the context above to craft a reply
    that sounds like a real friend texting back"]

    LLM --> REPLY["Buddy Sends a Text Back via SMS
    ────────────────────
    Under 200 tokens
    Plain text, no formatting
    Casual SMS style, stays in character
    Saved to chat history for future context"]

    REPLY --> USER

    %% =================== STYLING ===================
    classDef dbStyle fill:#3498db,stroke:#2471a3,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px
    classDef memStyle fill:#8e44ad,stroke:#6c3483,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px
    classDef blockStyle fill:#27ae60,stroke:#1e8449,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px
    classDef flowStyle fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#c0392b,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px
    classDef outputStyle fill:#f39c12,stroke:#d68910,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px

    class DB dbStyle
    class AI_MEMORY memStyle
    class B1,B2,B3,B4,B5,B6,B7,B8 blockStyle
    class USER,BACKEND,GATHER flowStyle
    class ASSEMBLED,LLM,REPLY outputStyle
